199
00:12:52,897 --> 00:12:55,191
The members currently assigned are

200
00:12:55,274 --> 00:13:01,280
Nishikaji, Otani, Kojima,
me, and Uchihara.

201
00:13:01,364 --> 00:13:05,284
Once we work out the details,
I'd like to have another meeting.

202
00:13:07,495 --> 00:13:10,498
{\an8}MARUNOUCHI, TOKYO

203
00:13:21,426 --> 00:13:23,428
{\an8}-How are you?
-How are you?

204
00:13:24,053 --> 00:13:26,138
{\an8}TADAMICHI KAWANO, M.D.
YURIKO'S EX-BOYFRIEND

205
00:13:26,222 --> 00:13:27,557
{\an8}-Did you wait long?
-No, not at all.

206
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:30,226
-I went ahead and sat.
-Oh, that's all right.

207
00:13:31,143 --> 00:13:33,187
I thought you'd bring me a Hepalyse.

208
00:13:34,731 --> 00:13:36,441
It's seriously been awhile.

209
00:13:36,524 --> 00:13:39,777
You've been busy, right?
What department are you in now?

210
00:13:39,861 --> 00:13:41,404
Nephrology now.

211
00:13:41,488 --> 00:13:43,155
-Oh, really?
-Yeah.

212
00:13:43,239 --> 00:13:44,949
Are you pretty busy, too?

213
00:13:46,158 --> 00:13:50,997
Mmm, exams are coming... in a week.

214
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,332
-In a week?
-What? Yes.

215
00:13:53,416 --> 00:13:56,002
Are you ready for them?

216
00:13:58,921 --> 00:14:00,715
-Look so good.
-Yeah.

217
00:14:00,798 --> 00:14:02,759
-You like bagna càuda, right?
-Yeah.

218
00:14:02,842 --> 00:14:04,886
-You liked it, right?
-Yeah.

219
00:14:04,969 --> 00:14:06,471
I remember it...

220
00:14:08,681 --> 00:14:10,933
It's been awhile
since I've had such good food.

221
00:14:12,477 --> 00:14:14,687
You usually don't eat much?

222
00:14:14,771 --> 00:14:16,773
I rarely eat out.

223
00:14:16,856 --> 00:14:18,400
At the hospital?

224
00:14:18,483 --> 00:14:21,361
I've eaten most of the food
delivered to the hospital.

225
00:14:21,444 --> 00:14:23,154
Of course.

226
00:14:32,288 --> 00:14:33,748
-You surprised me.
-Where are you looking?

227
00:14:33,831 --> 00:14:35,750
This way, please.

228
00:14:38,169 --> 00:14:41,589
-Head massage and treatment, right?
-Yes, please.

229
00:14:41,673 --> 00:14:44,008
"Yes, please"?

230
00:14:44,091 --> 00:14:46,177
I'll take care of you.

231
00:14:48,430 --> 00:14:51,641
-What? What?
-I get to see you work.

232
00:14:51,724 --> 00:14:53,435
This is embarrassing.

233
00:15:20,294 --> 00:15:23,339
