-No, it feels nice.

234
00:15:35,935 --> 00:15:38,646
The massage is done.

235
00:15:41,190 --> 00:15:42,233
Relaxed?

236
00:15:42,316 --> 00:15:44,819
Relaxed. It felt really good.

237
00:15:49,073 --> 00:15:50,450
It's so soft.

238
00:15:51,868 --> 00:15:54,912
-Silky, right?
